#

Masala Dosa with Coconut Chutney

45 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Indian

Course:

BreakfastSnack

Tags:

IndianBreakfastVegan

Description

Crispy rice crepes filled with spiced potatoes, served with refreshing coconut chutney.

Ingredients

  • dosa batter: 2 cups
  • potatoes: 2 medium, boiled and mashed
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • mustard seeds: 1 tsp
  • curry leaves: 8-10 leaves
  • turmeric powder: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • coconut (fresh grated): 1 cup
  • green chilies: 2, chopped
  • ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • coriander leaves: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • oil: for cooking
